---
import { site } from "../config";
---

<section class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-2xl flex-col gap-10 px-4 py-8 sm:gap-16 sm:py-12">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-pretty text-ink-1">Written for radio, not bullet points.</h2>
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium text-pretty text-ink-4">
      Claude summarises each article into a natural script that flows, then reads it in a clear voice.
    </h3>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-px rounded-xl border md:-mx-6">
    <div class="col-span-full flex flex-col gap-6 overflow-hidden rounded-[12px] p-6 md:flex-row md:items-start md:gap-10">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 md:w-2/5 md:shrink-0">
        <span class="text-2xl" aria-hidden="true">{site.mark}</span>
        <h3 class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-ink-1">Today's Recap</h3>
        <p class="text-lg leading-[1.4] font-medium text-pretty text-ink-3">
          Five stories from your queue, plus the topics you follow — in about seven minutes.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative max-h-56 flex-1 md:max-h-60">
        <div class="rounded-xl rounded-br-lg bg-elevated shadow-sm ring-[0.5px] ring-line md:translate-x-10">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b px-3 py-2">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-2">Friday · 5 stories · 7 min</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 p-5">
            <div class="flex gap-2.5">
              <div class="size-5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-surface-2"></div>
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-1">Good morning. Here's what you saved yesterday.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-2.5">
              <div class="shrink-0 text-base leading-none">{site.mark}</div>
              <div class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 flex-col gap-2">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-ink-3">
                  <span>Reading from your queue</span>
                  <span class="text-ink-4">5 articles</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-2">
                  First up, the state of AI agents in 2026 — the big shift this year is from
                  single prompts to long-running tasks. Then, why interest rates moved this
                  week, and what it means for borrowers…
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 border-t px-4 py-3">
            <button class="grid size-7 flex-none place-items-center rounded-full bg-palette-800 text-[11px] text-palette-50">▶</button>
            <div class="h-1 flex-1 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-surface-2">
              <div class="h-full w-1/3 rounded-full bg-palette-400"></div>
            </div>
            <span class="text-[12px] tabular-nums text-ink-3">2:14 / 7:02</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
